claim.claim-text:
A method of controlling a plurality of mobile terminals (200, 201, 202, 203) connected to an externally connected image display device (100), the method comprising:
transmitting screen information from a first mobile terminal (201) to the image display device (100) ;
transmitting screen information from a second mobile terminal (202) to the image display device (100);
displaying a first mirroring screen (101) corresponding to the screen information of the first mobile terminal (201) in a first region of a display of the image display device (100), and displaying a second mirroring screen (102) corresponding to the screen information of the second mobile terminal (202) in a second region of the display of the image display device (100);
tracking a cursor (156) on the display of the image display device (100) input from an input unit (155) of the image display device; and
controlling the first mobile terminal (201) from the image display device (100) when the cursor (156) is within the first region (101) of the display and controlling the second mobile terminal (202) from the image display device (100) when the cursor (156) is within the second region (102) of the display.
